sentences: He graduated from the Verdi Conservatory in Milan in 1928, having studied composition and conducting as well as honing his skills at the piano.
In Italy he performed a broad range of music, from pop to jazz and classical, and in 1938 led his first radio orchestra in Italy.
The program first aired on BBC Radio in 1957 and continued for around 25 years.
In 2015 Vocalion Records released a CD of his late 1950s broadcasts with the BBC Revue Orchestra, most of which had not been heard since their first broadcast.
In the late 1950s he also featured regularly at the Sanremo Music Festival.

sentences: Alberto Fernando Riccardo Semprini (27 March 1908 – 19 January 1990) known by his stage name Semprini, was an English pianist, composer and conductor, known for his appearances on the BBC, mainly on radio.
The program first aired on BBC Radio in 1957 and continued for around 25 years.
In 2015 Vocalion Records released a CD of his late 1950s broadcasts with the BBC Revue Orchestra, most of which had not been heard since their first broadcast.
